Name: UCSB
Description: A great University located along the California coast!

Name: Eiffel Tower
Description: A colossal landmark where I fell in love for the first time. With a great patch of grass below to watch the lights shine!

Name: Tecate
Description: A city on the border of Mexico that is full of culture and great food. My family has a home hear that goes back generations!

Name: Family Home
Description: This location has so many nostaligic memories and was the home I spent my high school years. It is a home in a coldasac with a half acre and a movie room, what more could you need!

Name: RSCS
Description: An excellent high school, but a small building with a triangle shaped parking lot.

Name: I.V. Deli Mart
Description: The first place I ate it in Isla Vista. A small deli with an excellent order of buffalo fries and a small seating area.
